Seachrome Coast is $17. Darkslick Shores is $18. Not really meaningful except that it's a counterpoint to pro-mythic zealots who said manabases would be super cheap now.Obviously you could have gotten them for less early on. But when people were shelling out $20 for shocklands, they weren't doing it just because they knew current lands would rotate in a year but because they were the best lands since 1993 and were probably as good as things were ever going to get. So probably not the best benchmark by those using "mythic=cheaper lands" argument.
